title: Gunmart - April 2016
description:
English | 292 pages | PDF | 116.8 MB

Gun Mart magazine is the biggest and most diverse shooting publication in the UK. The only magazine that caters to sports shooting, gun collecting and the militaria market, Gun Mart magazine is the most comprehensive title in its field. Established over 25 years ago, Gun Mart magazine has more than ten gun tests in every issue. Every issue of Gun Mart magazine features expert gun reviews and also includes:
- Country and Shotgun â€“ tests, reviews and news plus a Clay Shooting Ground Guide and major event coverage.
- Firearms â€“ Reviews of hunting and target air rifles plus everything from ammunition to scopes and reloading equipment.
- Airguns - hunting and target rifle reviews, air and CO2 pistol reviews, lamping and nightvision, scopes and more.
- Militaria Mart - geared towards antique weapons collecting, re-enactment and military history.
- Field Cutlery - four pages of knives and other edged tools.
- Practical & Tactical - a monthly round-up of equipment and clothing for heavy duty outdoor sports and pursuits, military and law enforcement
